[Recently, a moose was found in Nebraska. This is an unusual occurrence in
itself, but the moose was emaciated and died. The moose has caused NGPC to
wonder why the moose was in Nebraska but, also, could it have had CWD.
Tests are being conducted. CWD has not been seen in moose. The rise in CWD
in Nebraska is concerning. - Mod.TG
